{"tid":2295819,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"弄巧成拙的眼鏡蛇效應","createTime":"2020-11-22T04:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T10:21:31.000Z","uid":35357,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c86bc9a0accba8825033f97ca84cfe72bb39e152","tid":2295819,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"這是英殖印度時的一則趣聞，當時英政府計劃要減少當地眼鏡蛇數量，所以頒布了一條法令，指明每打死一條眼鏡蛇可以獲取賞金，聽起來好像是個不錯的方案，能動用群眾力量解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n不過，當時印度人為了獲取更多獎金，於是自己養殖眼鏡蛇，以確保獎金來源。當政府意識到這個問題，便取消獎金制度，令養蛇的人將蛇放回去，最後令眼鏡蛇數量急速上升。<br />\n<br />\n以上事件雖然只是一件趣聞，但在法國殖民越南時，就有歷史記載過類似的事件。<br />\n<br />\n當時河內鼠患嚴重，所以法國政府提出了一個獎金計劃，只要將老鼠殺死，將尾巴交給政府就可以獲取獎金。很多人只將老鼠尾巴斬走，再將老鼠放回下水道，令老鼠可以大量繁殖，同時增加捕鼠器銷售，令問題更嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n現在這個用字通常會用於形容錯誤的政治或經濟政策帶來更嚴重的問題了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://beginneros.com/triviaDetail.php?trivia_id=376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeginneros.com%2FtriviaDetail.php%3Ftrivia_id%3D376&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r8ljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=1ff1b3f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beginneros.com/triviaDetail.php?trivia_id=376</a><br />\n<br />\n確診數字gogogo!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8809325765233aeb45cd42f6b70059627500a9","tid":2295819,"uid":35357,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"仲有另一個term<br />\nPerverse incentive<br />\n<br />\n有興趣自己Google"},{"pid":"74baac47fbe7c4d43949635e51b2215ea77b7867","tid":2295819,"uid":137560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"確診肺炎有$5000"},{"pid":"2ce8b189c6c6ed933ba6318f5f124335ce6bf973","tid":2295819,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ee06e3d36e10b0cec860d776bd52459a2e0b9","tid":2295819,"uid":86509,"like":0,"disl